<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM14.4">
<l>kārttaṇ kamalak kaṇṇeṉṉu neṭuṅka yiṟupa ṭuttiyeṉṉai</l>
<l>yīrttuk koṇṭu viḷaiyāṭu mīcaṉ ṟaṉṉaik kaṇṭīrē</l>
<l>pōrtta muttiṉ kuppāyap pukarmāl yāṉaik kaṉṟēpōl</l>
<l>vērttu niṉṟu viḷaiyāṭa viruntā vaṉattē kaṇṭōmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Did you see the Supreme Lord who plays by tying me with a long rope</l>
<l>That is [His] rainy, cool, lotus eyes, and dragging [me] along?</l>
<l>We saw Him play in Bṛndāvana sweating like a dark, lustrous elephant calf</l>
<l>Covered in a coat made of pearls!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
